      "para_id": "Q001116.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(Main Text, 1) For Ninĝirsu of the E-ninnu , Dudu , the temple administrator of Ninĝirsu , transported ( this material ) from Arawa , and fashioned this ( plaque ) for ( using it with ) the roof-beam nails ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001116.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(Caption 1, 1) Dudu , the exalted temple administrator of Ninĝirsu ."
    }
  ],
